  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to compare the touch-screen version of the PFDI-20, PFIQ-7, PISQ
      12 and SF-36 french questionnaires to their paper versions. The investigators hypothesize
      that the percentage of completely filled questionnaires will be higher in the touch-screen
      version.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
